First, ensure that there is an odd number of exits. If there 
aren't any,  swim up. If you can't swim up then take any exit and 
swim up. Then swim through all the corners (NW, SW, NE ans SE) in 
turn that are open. If you went through all corners, you can swim 
up. This is the way out.

